# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
## [4.0.0]
#	+ Binary file & binary output
#	+ Boost Program Options
#	- Remove Microsoft Windows support
#	- Remove TUI
#	- Remove Safety Encrypt OHCS
## [3.0.0]
### Added
#	+ Binary file support
#	+ All encoding support
### Changed
#	- CANNOT Decrypt <= 2.1.0 file
## [2.1.0]
### Added
#	+ OpenMP support
#	+ Unix TUI (ncurses) support
### Changed
#	- Safety Encrypt OHCS changed to OPTIONAL
#	- UTF-8 Encrypt fail bug fixed
## [2.0.1] - 2018-02-19
### Changed
#	- UTF-8 null line bug fixed
## [2.0.0] - 2018-02-19
### Added
#	+ UTF-8 support
### Change
#	- CAN NOT ENCRYPT/DECRYPT 1.x DATA
## [1.6] - 2018-02-17
### Added
#	+ Safety Encrypt OHCS

## [1.5] - 2018-02-16
### Added
#	+ GNU Make support
#	+ CMake support
#	+ Visual Studio C++ support
#	+ GNU C++ Compiler support
#	+ Clang C++ Compiler support
#	+ new debug option
#	+ Features on UNIX
#		+ GNU style Option support (long option)
#		+ POSIX style Option support (short option)
#		+ Read File support
#	+ Features on Windows
#		+ Command line interface support
### Changed

### Removed
